{"tid":1047481,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖有適當既隱瞞係咪對大家都好？","createTime":"2019-03-05T03:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T06:08:10.000Z","uid":200417,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce76e5b59ba882a401588ec78c36046a3b6f77e","tid":1047481,"uid":200417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:42:23.000Z","msg":"與女朋友拍拖兩年幾，都一齊住左年幾。<br />\n<br />\n我知道佢既過去，以前佢同A拍拖時，同B有親密關係。<br />\n佢同我講同A相處咩都限住哂，A唔鍾意佢同隊友食飯、玩。就算俾佢去都會好早係地鐵等佢，令佢覺得有壓力、無自由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢同左我一齊後，同時出咗黎做野，個人比起以前係定性咗，以前既佢只有佢發人脾氣，而家會遷就，唔會一面倒佢食住人。咩都以我為先，同佢啲朋友玩、食飯都會預我，除非係我唔想去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但自己成日都唔信人（其實只係唔鍾意佢同B有交流），我成日都唔鍾意佢去食飯既地方有B, 因為我知佢有時都會關心B, 佢份人都係會關心人男女都會關，抵得諗。    <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近B開Post拍拖，我同佢同時見到個Post, 唔知咩磁場加直覺都覺得佢唔開心，而我地久唔久因為B而鬧交。 佢見到post就話佢無野，有啲驚訝姐。<br />\n其後我衰仔偷睇佢電話，見到佢同老死講「有失戀既感覺」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時鬧交，因為佢有啲位隱瞞我，因為知我知道好會發脾氣唔開心，但我講話我唔介意佢同任何人玩，只介意佢隱瞞或同啲過去有關係或者曾經鍾意/好感既人玩，想佢坦誠，是咪好霸道....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知應該點好，尋求開解。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923aba952813d340621c6ca990e62bf6e8a3ade4","tid":1047481,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bec6fba068364307fcc16f178096abd1e383bc3","tid":1047481,"uid":238986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:46:25.000Z","msg":"基本啦 識撈 大家都開心"},{"pid":"c02986f9d9b8bb2c9ac5d3820a257584fb86f0b6","tid":1047481,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"一定係"},{"pid":"807ec34d9c3525c899147906f74253fe38d60fe8","tid":1047481,"uid":108606,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:47:06.000Z","msg":"張敬軒都有歌唱：切勿誠實交往 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：a0 兵仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82cb7bfbab5ce2c09217f8a11a43b779a5d1474","tid":1047481,"uid":111322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:47:25.000Z","msg":"結咗婚都一樣"},{"pid":"65c632f438f1039368d7ad1d5e3ffb54ff0a5439","tid":1047481,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:47:55.000Z","msg":"同你好熟咩 乜都同你講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2758327bab3a4699b6ec27ab54fced1aef49feb9","tid":1047481,"uid":90646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"點解要手多睇人信息 好多野唔知好過知"},{"pid":"a90c279919f5d9c3f2ab3c9878b7c915228f3b7b","tid":1047481,"uid":200417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:48:05.000Z","msg":"成日提自己 愈束搏佢 愈快走，<br />\n個腦成日都好清楚邊啲應該做邊啲唔應該迫佢，但都忍唔住做咗，例如睇電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386691c40a0dc97b51827d9adc4293f8c76d6c15","tid":1047481,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:48:10.000Z","msg":"每個人都有一定既私隱"},{"pid":"6b634c2c26c82f8c563ec9a01977194f05e51379","tid":1047481,"uid":152701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:59:57.000Z","msg":"無病呻吟嘅東亞病夫<br />\n學下長大啦 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f770af03426a3bd240897467973f1e99e34dd43","tid":1047481,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"無論熱戀中失戀中 都永遠記住第一戒"},{"pid":"b9f329aaa6e4ddff221b2a6a480b6b959df8b6de","tid":1047481,"uid":79023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:06:01.000Z","msg":"又愛又恨咁先正<br />\n感情要拉拉扯扯，高低起伏<br />\n之後睇番好似打機過左幾關咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d8b77abb27402234cdf31a46f17e35476b3765","tid":1047481,"uid":94483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"其實你講緊乜鳩？"},{"pid":"e1bce7b99a931b80ef1cbdd8650b039dacfd320d","tid":1047481,"uid":222779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2d8b77abb27402234cdf31a46f17e35476b3765","tid":1047481,"uid":94483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"其實你講緊乜鳩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"係你個腦有事定我地有事？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585a339feb2fd88bbe5e487ef0892bec912b67c4","tid":1047481,"uid":164863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:07:18.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得拍拖一心一意真係好重要<br />\n如果佢係三心兩意<br />\n同你一齊又諗住第二個<br />\n其實佢唔方好得去邊<br />\n如果係我 我諗我好快會淡"},{"pid":"3cd5052bdf8edbeb5b31b39ba44437cc2a0a7f6e","tid":1047481,"uid":19463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:08:10.000Z","msg":"屌"}]}